newsitem.title: USA: CBOT OVERNIGHT PROJECT A AG VOLUME 2,191 CONTRACTS.
newsitem.headline: CBOT OVERNIGHT PROJECT A AG VOLUME 2,191 CONTRACTS.

text.p: Chicago Board of Trade said its Project A overnight agricultural trading volume totaled 2,191 contracts compared with 1,862 overnight Sunday.
There were 184 wheat, 1,162 corn, 543 soybean, 40 soymeal, 71 soyoil, 11 oat, 90 corn calls, two corn puts, 26 soybean calls and 62 soybean puts traded.
In overnight trading, wheat was two to three cents higher, corn was 3-3/4 to 6-1/2 cents higher and soybeans were three to 6-1/4 cents higher.
